01:21:13.417 --> 01:21:15.542
That's the one you like.

01:21:16.958 --> 01:21:20.292
Let's go. Let's go.

01:21:24.167 --> 01:21:27.917
What do you had for lunch? Oh my God.

01:21:32.542 --> 01:21:36.291
Don't wait for us. Manuela and I
