01:21:51.917 --> 01:21:56.875
Who's in charge of this castle?
Who's the boss here?

01:21:57.292 --> 01:21:58.042
You, boss.

01:21:58.083 --> 01:22:00.374
See that's what I like to hear.
Open the door.

