01:24:42.250 --> 01:24:45.333
And I get a break from
the telephone threats.

01:24:48.833 --> 01:24:50.667
All set ma'am.

01:24:55.958 --> 01:24:58.749
Was it a new number?

01:24:58.750 --> 01:25:01.125
But not for long.

