01:43:07.750 --> 01:43:11.166
The family is bait.
We need them alive and at home.

01:43:11.167 --> 01:43:13.624
Put them some place, we sit
and we wait.

01:43:13.625 --> 01:43:17.667
Pablo will try to talk to them, right?
When that happens, we'll be ready.

